igns</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/dupuytrens-disease/references/\">Auld, 2017</a>]; the British Medical Journal (BMJ) best practice guide <em>Dupuytren's contracture</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/dupuytrens-disease/references/\">BMJ, 2019</a>]; and the National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE) interventional procedures guideline <em>Radiation therapy for early Dupuytren's disease</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/dupuytrens-disease/references/\">NICE, 2016</a>].</div><!-- end field 28e36122-829b-406b-badb-ac7000f3a3a4 --><!-- end item 9091066d-2f49-4284-a8c1-081117143a75 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}